[
  {
    "text": "Well here we are. The location of the\nsoul stone is right in there.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "duration": 5.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I guess you better go in and get it.",
    "start": 6.4,
    "duration": 4.34
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a lake of acid lava.",
    "start": 10.74,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I know crazy right?!",
    "start": 12.64,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, hop on in and get that stone you need so bad.",
    "start": 14.78,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "It's all the way at the bottom.",
    "start": 18.54,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Bubbles",
    "start": 20.12,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Crap! You and your stinking bubbles!",
    "start": 21.12,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "You lied to me again.",
    "start": 23.72,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "What?! That's crazy.",
    "start": 25.22,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "You must have turned it to bubbles.",
    "start": 27.02,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean I wouldn't lie to you.",
    "start": 28.7,
    "duration": 1.659
  },
  {
    "text": "Your sister will pay for this.",
    "start": 30.36,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh my gosh Thanos!\nThe sister has escaped!",
    "start": 32.7,
    "duration": 3.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Dangit! You guys had one job!",
    "start": 36.16,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "This does not put a smile on my face.",
    "start": 38.92,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh no! Why? Why would you do that?! Too soon!!!! Nooo!",
    "start": 63.98,
    "duration": 5.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Strange! You alright?",
    "start": 73.12,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "I just went forward in time to see all the possible outcomes.",
    "start": 75.8,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Well how many do we win?",
    "start": 78.94,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Five.",
    "start": 81.72,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh yeah. You're much more of a Thanos.",
    "start": 85.04,
    "duration": 3.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I take it Maw is dead then.",
    "start": 88.66,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "At least he accomplished his mission.",
    "start": 91.0,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Cloak of levitation!",
    "start": 92.34,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "What is this?",
    "start": 93.22,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And sling ring. And cut!",
    "start": 93.92,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow!",
    "start": 97.06,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That was awesome!",
    "start": 97.56,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice job Sherlock!",
    "start": 98.4,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Did we win already?!",
    "start": 99.48,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "He is very strong!!",
    "start": 103.62,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "And... Baby Thanos!",
    "start": 106.7,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Baby noises...",
    "start": 110.72,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay now we can kill him.",
    "start": 115.94,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "We can't kill Thanos now! He's just a baby!",
    "start": 117.54,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Well who's gonna take care of him? We can't just leave him here!",
    "start": 121.32,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey honey! Remember that dream I was",
    "start": 125.2,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "talking about having a baby?",
    "start": 127.26,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Say hello to our new son Thanos!",
    "start": 129.44,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Dadadadada!",
    "start": 131.84,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh come on! This is not the weirdest thing I've brought home before!",
    "start": 133.76,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell me you didn't do it!",
    "start": 138.98,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I had to...",
    "start": 140.46,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "No you didn't!",
    "start": 141.82,
    "duration": 0.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Is there anyone else NOT using their hands at the moment",
    "start": 142.58,
    "duration": 2.34
  },
  {
    "text": "that could shut him up!!",
    "start": 145.02,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you!",
    "start": 147.8,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "It's almost there! I've almost got it!",
    "start": 149.28,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The power of the gauntlet now rests on\nnew shoulders.",
    "start": 165.02,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Anything I yearn for is within my grasp.",
    "start": 169.02,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "You know what I yearn for dear Thanos?",
    "start": 174.02,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh dang.",
    "start": 177.9,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Revenge!",
    "start": 179.02,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Sweet.",
    "start": 186.34,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay I'm done!",
    "start": 188.48,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Dibs!",
    "start": 190.06,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Nonono! I don't think so!",
    "start": 190.78,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll be taking that, thanks.",
    "start": 191.94,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "This will be the end of Wakanda.",
    "start": 198.66,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Then it will be the noblest ending in history.",
    "start": 200.74,
    "duration": 2.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't worry everyone. I've got this!",
    "start": 204.84,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Mirror Dimension!",
    "start": 207.56,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "And gone!",
    "start": 211.92,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 214.42,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wong!",
    "start": 215.8,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "THANOS!",
    "start": 221.76,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "I told you, you would die for that.",
    "start": 230.12,
    "duration": 2.34
  },
  {
    "text": "You should have aimed for the head.",
    "start": 233.22,
    "duration": 3.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I know. I was thinking the exact same thing.",
    "start": 236.76,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "But then I thought...",
    "start": 239.94,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Naaaahhh!",
    "start": 241.38,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "The arm is good.",
    "start": 242.46,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh poop.",
    "start": 244.76,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "And so I defeated Thanos because I am truly awesome.",
    "start": 247.54,
    "duration": 3.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I have this amazing new axe.",
    "start": 250.78,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "The rabbit gave me a new eyeball from his buttocks.",
    "start": 253.0,
    "duration": 2.42
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm the rightful king of Asgard.",
    "start": 255.96,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Which is now Earth by the way. I forgot to mention that.",
    "start": 258.42,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "So I suppose that makes me your new ruler...",
    "start": 262.14,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Sooo...",
    "start": 266.38,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You're welcome!",
    "start": 267.82,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "What did he say?",
    "start": 270.36,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Is he talking to the whole table, because I wasn't listening.",
    "start": 271.4,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you speak up!?",
    "start": 273.48,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "I said I'm your new ruler!",
    "start": 274.28,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, Earth doesn't work like that I'm afraid.",
    "start": 276.08,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, me and my new Infinity gauntlet beg to differ.",
    "start": 278.24,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I will follow the majestic pirate angel man anywhere!",
    "start": 280.64,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Well I won't! Hey jerk face, my girlfriend\ndied for your precious gauntlet!",
    "start": 283.42,
    "duration": 4.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, you mean this girlfriend?",
    "start": 288.02,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Woah. Where am I?",
    "start": 290.58,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Awesome!",
    "start": 292.54,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "There is Gamora!!",
    "start": 293.48,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay! I take it back.",
    "start": 294.4,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "That Thor guy is pretty great.",
    "start": 296.18,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Well you guys...",
    "start": 298.08,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "We finally made it.",
    "start": 299.56,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "What an achievement right?",
    "start": 300.76,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at us. Everyone's here!",
    "start": 302.52,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "The Guardians...",
    "start": 304.86,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Spider-man.",
    "start": 305.92,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Shuri even made a new Vision.",
    "start": 307.38,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you Vibranium!",
    "start": 308.98,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, everyone's here except Hawkeye. And the Netflix Avengers.",
    "start": 310.8,
    "duration": 3.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And Antman.",
    "start": 314.56,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "My bad guys! Siri didn't know how to get to Wakanda!",
    "start": 315.64,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. Except those guys.",
    "start": 319.06,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "We're all here though!",
    "start": 321.9,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And we won the day!",
    "start": 323.1,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you talking about? We always win.",
    "start": 324.1,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "This is like every summer for us!",
    "start": 325.62,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you imagine if we actually lost?",
    "start": 327.82,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Laughing...",
    "start": 331.54,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "People would be emotionally scarred for life!",
    "start": 333.38,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "I literally just became the King of Wakanda!",
    "start": 335.06,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Well thanks to us... and mostly me...",
    "start": 337.72,
    "duration": 1.88
  },
  {
    "text": "we didn't lose. Sooo...",
    "start": 339.6,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "A toast!",
    "start": 341.1,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's to the greatest team in the whole universe!",
    "start": 342.36,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "YEAH!!!!",
    "start": 345.24,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "To vibranium!",
    "start": 346.44,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Vibranium! Yeah!",
    "start": 347.76,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "And to a couple of tagalongs who are pretty awesome as well.",
    "start": 349.16,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Here here! Yeah!",
    "start": 352.0,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you talking about us?",
    "start": 354.62,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not a tag-along I was here first.",
    "start": 355.62,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, if anything you guys are all my third wheel?",
    "start": 357.7,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you know why?",
    "start": 360.32,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "BECAUSE YOU'RE BATMAN!",
    "start": 361.24,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Hehe!",
    "start": 363.72,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right.",
    "start": 364.66,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I'm Batman.",
    "start": 366.1,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "I am Groot.",
    "start": 367.44,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Batman!",
    "start": 368.6,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 371.78,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I really thought that was gonna come back to me.",
    "start": 372.28,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a teenager. He doesn't care about anything right now.",
    "start": 373.74,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Well I guess I win then.",
    "start": 376.9,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I'm Batman.",
    "start": 378.7,
    "duration": 0.58
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Steve Rogers.",
    "start": 379.28,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Dangit!",
    "start": 380.28,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Please stop.",
    "start": 380.78,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey! Remember when we had that Civil War?",
    "start": 382.08,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "And wanted to kill each other for nothing?",
    "start": 384.96,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahahaha!",
    "start": 386.68,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "I got paralyzed.",
    "start": 388.62,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "We were all arrested.",
    "start": 390.14,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when Rhodes had a different face?",
    "start": 391.58,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when Bruce had a different face?!",
    "start": 393.4,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey remember when Black Widow made me believe we had a future together?",
    "start": 394.94,
    "duration": 3.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahaha, she did!!",
    "start": 398.44,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Burn!",
    "start": 399.62,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when I saved the world from Dormamu without any of you?",
    "start": 400.78,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't make us stories Strange!",
    "start": 404.36,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahahahaha!",
    "start": 406.44,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not making it up.",
    "start": 408.94,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when I killed Tony's parents?",
    "start": 409.96,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm still not 100% okay with that you one armed Jesus!",
    "start": 412.34,
    "duration": 2.78
  },
  {
    "text": "I have two arms you- WAIT?!",
    "start": 415.68,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "What?!",
    "start": 417.32,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahah, I told you I'd get that arm!",
    "start": 418.22,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahahahaha!",
    "start": 420.28,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Silly rabbit, tricks are for wizards!",
    "start": 422.38,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Hahahaha!",
    "start": 424.62,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Happy endings are so cheesy sometimes.",
    "start": 431.42,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey man. My name's Korg and this is my very good friend Meek.",
    "start": 433.66,
    "duration": 3.86
  },
  {
    "text": "We're gonna go to that jukebox over there and play some music.",
    "start": 437.82,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Wanna come?",
    "start": 440.86,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Sure, why not?",
    "start": 443.22,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I was all... Tank Missle!",
    "start": 445.08,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when Starlord used to be immortal?",
    "start": 447.2,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember when I was frozen?!",
    "start": 449.76,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Has anyone else been to the ancestral plane?",
    "start": 451.02,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone want to buy a robot arm?",
    "start": 452.84,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "What about the spider-kid?",
    "start": 454.68,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Does he need a robot arm?",
    "start": 456.04,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh I like this tune.",
    "start": 457.04,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "It has a nice beat.",
    "start": 458.7,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "What did you just do?!?!?",
    "start": 464.02,
    "duration": 2.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You lost?!?!?",
    "start": 468.4,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I did.",
    "start": 470.18,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Does that mean I won the bet?",
    "start": 471.94,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo hoo!",
    "start": 474.2,
    "duration": 0.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys?",
    "start": 474.94,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel... itchy. Like really weird.",
    "start": 476.02,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Woah.",
    "start": 481.98,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Curses!",
    "start": 484.42,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh no! This is different.",
    "start": 486.34,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Noooo!",
    "start": 488.68,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Something's happening-",
    "start": 491.2,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Gasp!",
    "start": 492.46,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "On your feet old man.",
    "start": 494.8,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "This is no place to-",
    "start": 495.94,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Boss?",
